00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:30,200
VHS was the first second chance

485
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,080
for those films,

486
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,600
and it created an appreciation

487
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,040
for these kinds of story

